title: Prodeus: The Elder Veil - Official Announcement Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
description:
Prodeus: The Elder Veil is a DLC expansion to the retro first-person shooter action game developed by Bounding Box Software Inc. Explore a new Greek-inspired environment with plenty of enemies to dispatch and weapons to use while airborne thanks to a trusty deployable chain for traversal. Prodeus: The Elder Veil DLC is coming soon for Prodeus on PC.

#ProdeusTheElderVeil #RealmsDeep2023

title: Why Live-Service Games Are a Bigger Gamble For Devs Than Players - Beyond Clips
description:
With the recent layoffs at Naughty Dog and the future of The Last of Us Multiplayer "on thin ice", the Podcast Beyond crew discuss how live-service games are a big gamble for devs. We also explore some successes among other game studios and other live-service games that didn't make it. From Fortnite to Hyenas, it's always going to be unpredictable when you enter the space of Games as a Service.

#LiveServiceGams #Beyond #BeyondClips
